Subject: ignore LAPS check
Description:
hi, 
One of my customer use Windows LAPS in the cloud but PingCastle inform to install LAPS.  I don't know how to ignore this check to make it disapear from the pingCastle Report.
Thanks.
Solution_Comment__c:
Currently the only way to exclude this is the following.

Work around is to generate the report with --level Full so the xml data contains all the data, edit the xml, then regenerate the report based on the xml data with the option --regen-report <file.xml>
